commit.message:
Removing the sample plot.html

Don't really need it, people can see the .png graphs and generate it using example_backtest

Added in a bunch of comments; backtest now takes in plot_args and only plots 1 data point every plot_freq (used to be print_freq) instead of having a fixed stride length of 100. Fixed logic for EMA, though the algorithm seem to not always perform better (the previous logic was flawed though, as it never kept correct count of the trend but instead bought when there were a lot of fluxation and rapid crossover, rather than when it's a big upward/downward trend (TODO: why did that work??). \nexample_backtests now seed to 1 by default (to get deterministic results)
Fixed some example backtests; updated Contributors & Readme
Added EMA to example strategies on README.md
